'''TSM''' is an [[:category:United States|American]] esports organization, created around the community website SoloMid.Net by brothers Andy '''"Reginald"''' Dinh and Dan '''"Dan Dinh"''' Dinh in September 2009.

==History==
The organization first entered the PUBG Mobile scene on the 3rd of March 2020 by collaborating with Indian esports organization '''''[https://www.instagram.com/entitygamingind/ Entity Gaming]''''', forming the IP ''[[TSM Entity]]''. Post the ban of '''''[[PUBG Mobile]]''''' in India and the eventual release of '''''[[Battlegrounds Mobile India]]''''', TSM parted ways with their roster and ended their partnership with ''Entity Gaming''. The organization announced its new BGMI roster on the 30th of July 2021.
