===Format===
'''''Upthrust Esports India Rising Series 2024:'''  March 5th - 28th, 2024
* '''Eliminator Week:''''' March 5th - 10th, 2024
** 32 teams , 6 matchdays.
*** 26 invited teams.
*** 6 qualified teams.
** Round-robin format; Teams are divided into 4 groups of 8.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 24 teams}} qualify for [[#Week 1 and 2|Week 1 and 2]].
<div style="margin-top:13px"></div>
* '''Week 1:''''' March 12th - 17th, 2024
** '''Qualifiers:''' March 12th - 15th
*** 24 teams , 4 matchdays
*** Round-robin format; Teams are divided into 3 groups of 8.
*** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} qualify for Week 1 Finals.
** '''Finals:''' March 16th - 17th
*** 16 teams , 2 matchdays
*** 12 matches (6 each day).
<div style="margin-top:13px"></div>
* '''Week 2:''''' March 19th - 24th, 2024
** '''Qualifiers:''' March 19th - 22th
*** 24 teams , 4 matchdays
*** Round-robin format; Teams are divided into 3 groups of 8.
*** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} qualify for Week 2 Finals.
** '''Finals:''' March 23th - 24th
*** 16 teams , 2 matchdays
*** 12 matches (6 each day). 
<div style="margin-top:13px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' March 26th - 28th, 2024
** 16 teams , 3 matchdays.
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|Top 16 teams}} according to the total points from Week 1 and 2 Qualifiers.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

